description: Lists all of the engagements to contact channels that have been acknowledged.

parameters.name: PageId
parameters.description: The Amazon Resource Name (ARN) of the engagement to a specific contact channel.

nested_items.name: NextToken
nested_items.description: The pagination token to continue to the next page of results.

nested_items.name: ContactChannelArn
nested_items.description: The Amazon Resource Name (ARN) of the contact channel Incident Manager engaged.

nested_items.name: ReceiptType
nested_items.description: The type follows the engagement cycle, SENT, DELIVERED, and READ.

nested_items.name: ReceiptInfo
nested_items.description: Information provided during the page acknowledgement.

nested_items.name: ReceiptTime
nested_items.description: The time receipt was SENT, DELIVERED, or READ.
